    Provides the builder process for creating instances of EmbeddedDerbyDatabase. The assumption is that the creation script only creates the tables with no constraints on keys. The insertion process can be either through Excel or a script having SQL insert statements. The alter script then places the key and other constraints on the database. We assume that valid data and scripts are in place.
